 The time has come to swallow our pride and admit our fault. The Emperor will convert to Catholicism and require everyone in the palace to do the same. We will fully embrace Union of Florence - Roma suprema est.  Your decision will cause anger among our priesthood and the nobles, but the Catholic nations will rejoice and we hope that the Pope shall call for a new crusade to save Constantinople. <br> \[Noble Support -20\] <br> \[Priest Support -30\] <br> \[Religion - the Great Schism is mended\]
